snippet.title: Re-Volt(RVGL): Two Neighborhoods, 16 Cars
snippet.description:
This is a track from Re-Volt World Summer Contest 2021, created by Keyran. This track uses Toys in the Hood tracks as a base. There is a road that joins the two original tracks(Toys in the Hood 1 and Toys in the Hood 2).

Track: Two Neighborhoods
Length: 1409 m
Laps: 4
